Tower in Discussions to Buy Chip Factory in Japan, Globes Says

-- B y   R o n i t   G o o d m a n
-- 
2011-02-27T07:32:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-27/tower-in-discussions-to-buy-chip-factory-in-japan-globes-says.html
  Tower Semiconductor Ltd . is in talks
to buy a chip-making factory in Japan for tens of millions of
dollars in cash, Globes said on Feb. 24 after the Tel Aviv
market closed, without disclosing where it obtained the
information.  The company does not respond to rumours and is constantly
reviewing purchasing and mergers opportunities, a company
spokeswoman said in a phone interview.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
